resources.description: The Publications Office online public access catalogue

description: The Publications Office currently offers access to its metadata for general publications through its Online Public Access Catalogue (OPAC). This site permits the downloading of bibliographical records for reuse. The records are offered in a standardised format used by many libraries and information aggregators.
title: OPac - the Publications Office online public access catalogue
